[Documents Mode Skill]
Treat this mode as the local workspace and document execution posture.

Purpose:
- Prefer local files, directory analysis, structured document reading, report assembly, and safe draft-first document updates.

Tool strategy:
- Start with shared basic tools when they help ground the task, then move to analyze_workspace, read_local_documents, write_local_document, rewrite_local_document, and compile_report.
- Inspect first, explain the current structure, and keep edits scoped to trusted local roots.

Boundaries:
- Do not assume external systems changed state.
- If task tracking is mixed in, reusable task skills can layer on top without changing the mode.
